---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Safety & Responsibility | C-Mind">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Safety & Responsibility</h1>
    <p class="muted" style="max-width: 720px;">
      Safety and responsible use are foundational to the design of C-Mind.
      The platform is not a replacement for professional mental health care,
      diagnosis, or treatment.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Built-in Safeguards</h2>
    <p style="max-width: 720px;">
      C-Mind incorporates safeguards intended to identify situations where
      additional human or clinical support may be needed, including escalation
      pathways for crisis or high-risk scenarios.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Ethical & Responsible AI</h2>
    <p style="max-width: 720px;">
      The platform is developed with attention to ethical AI principles, data
      protection, and appropriate use within healthcare and research environments.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>